'However, even after the establishment of that silencing, Thsp was able to support a stronger expression of the reporter gene and its promoter accumulated less DNA methylation.In this report, we show that the promoter of a terminatorless construct accumulates DNA methylation levels in the same range of those of constructs with good efficiency terminators, the methylation shows preference for the CG context and as a result, LUC expression is completely abolished.', 'By contrast, both terminators display a very distinct pattern of poly(A) sites, with mRNAs under the influence of tHSP being polyadenylated mainly at one site, whereas tNOS transcripts possess two principal regions where cleavage occurs.', 'Note that the U residues at positions −12 and −11 would always be present in the base of the terminator hairpin.', '(a) The region containing mapped poly(A) cleavage sites (CS) for each of the terminators used in the present study is depicted.', 'An intrinsic terminator contains a Sponsor/Collaborators: Washington University School of Medicine|Novartis Pharmaceuticals
